110
00:10:26,890 --> 00:10:30,080
…室内设计，律师或诸如此类
...interior designer or lawyer or something like that.

111
00:10:30,290 --> 00:10:33,090
我对我爸爸说我想以写作为业
I'd say to my dad, "I want to be a writer."

112
00:10:33,290 --> 00:10:35,020
