129
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:34,410
我讨厌这样
I hate it.

130
00:11:34,820 --> 00:11:36,410
非常反感
I really hate it.

131
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:40,420
知道吗，尽管这种种不快…
Well, you know, despite all that kind of bullshit...

132
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:42,290
…总是会随之而来
...that comes along with it...

133
00:11:42,860 --> 00:11:45,660
…但我记得童年就象…
...I remember childhood as...

134
00:11:46,530 --> 00:11:48,560
…一段魔幻时光
...this magical time.

135
00:11:48,770 --> 00:11:53,710
真的，记得我妈妈第一次跟我说到死亡
I do. I remember when my mother first told me about death.

136
00:11:53,970 --> 00:11:58,670
我的曾祖母去世，我们全家去弗罗里达奔丧
My great-grandmother had died, and my family had visited them in Florida.

137
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:00,940
当时我才三岁或三岁半
I was about 3, 3 1/2 years old.

138
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:04,580
我在后院玩耍时…
Anyway, I was in the back yard playing...

139
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:08,380
…姐姐教我怎样拿浇花的水管…
...and my sister had just taught me how to take the garden hose...

140
00:12:08,590 --> 00:12:10,750
…就是象这样子捏着…
...and do it in such a way that...

141
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:14,720
…喷出的水雾会在阳光下形成一道彩虹
...it sprayed into the sun and would make a rainbow.

142
00:12:16,230 --> 00:12:18,090
于是我那样做…
And so I was doing that...

143
00:12:18,330 --> 00:12:21,460
…透过水雾，我看到了曾祖母
...and through the mist,I could see my grandmother.

144
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:24,970
